After encountering a severe ion storm, the Enterprise visits Star Base 11 for repairs.
While there, Kirk files a report about the death of crewman and former friend LCDR
Finney, who was taking scientific readings in an externally mounted instrument pod
before Kirk needed to jettison it for the safety of the ship. However, the computer
log shows that Kirk jettisoned the pod before there was a danger, thereby revealing
the captain's willful perjury and culpable negligence in crewman Finney's death.
